rid]]\n|stadium=[[Santiago Bernab\u00e9u Stadium]] \n|attendance=100,000\n|referee={{flagicon|DDR}}[[Siegfried Kirschen]] \n|result=W \n}}\n\n====Semi-final====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round      = \n|date       = 6 April 1988\n|time       = 21:00 [[Central European Time|CET]]\n|team1      = [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]] {{flagicon|ESP}}\n|score      = 1\u20131\n|report     = [http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1987/matches/round=24/match=4082/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report] \n|team2      = {{flagicon|NED}} [[PSV Eindhoven|PSV]]\n|goals1     = [[Hugo S\u00e1nchez|S\u00e1nchez]] {{goal|6}}\n|goals2     = [[Edward Linskens|Linskens]] {{goal|19}}<br>Van Aerle{{yel|55}}<br>[[Wim Kieft|Kieft]]{{yel|78}}\n|stadium    = [[Santiago Bernab\u00e9u Stadium]]\n|location   = [[Madrid]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|result     = D\n|stack      = Y\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round      = \n|date       = 20 April 1988\n|time       = 19:30 [[Central European Time|CET]]\n|team1      = [[PSV Eindhoven|PSV]] {{flagicon|NED}}\n|score      = 0\u20130\n|aggregatescore = 1[[Away goals rule|a]] \u20131\n|report     = [http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=1987/matches/round=24/match=4083/postmatch/lineups/index.html Report] \n|team2      = {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Real Madrid C.F.|Real Madrid]]\n|goals1     = Vanenburg{{yel|75}}\n|goals2     = Chendo{{yel|75}}\n|stadium    = [[Philips Stadion]]\n|location   = [[Eindhoven]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|result     = D\n}}\n\n== Statistics ==\n=== Squad statistics ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;width:60%;float:left;text-align:center;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | competition\n! rowspan=\"2\" | points\n! colspan=\"6\" | total\n! rowspan=\"2\" | [[goal diference|DR]]\n|-\n! {{Descrizione comando|G|Games played}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|V|Games won}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|N|Games drawed}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|P|Games lost}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|Gf|Goal scored}}\n! {{Descrizione comando|